of Madame Gaillard.

66
00:07:01,317 --> 00:07:06,297
- How many today?
- Four, well... three and a half.

67
00:07:10,245 --> 00:07:15,644
- As usual, more dead than alive.
- Just take the money and sign!

68
00:07:22,572 --> 00:07:26,173
- Make room!
- Where?

69
00:07:26,208 --> 00:07:27,113
